title: Wednesday Pt2: Week One Beefs, Brandon Marshall, Andre Reed, and MVP pick reaction
itunes:title: Wednesday Pt2: Week One Beefs, Brandon Marshall, Andre Reed, and MVP pick reaction
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with beefs for Week One.  Hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty continue Prediction Week with their nominees for Defensive Player of the Year.  6x Pro Bowl WR Brandon Marshall drops by to give his Top 5 WR list and what he remembers from his 21 catch game.  Hall of Famer Andrew Reed helps us preview Opening night between the Bills and Rams while hinting around Buffalo's interest in Odell Beckham Jr.  

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
